---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" currentPage="about">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>ABOUT</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="about-content">
    <p>
      I'm <strong>Alexander Vega</strong> — an independent developer working on infrastructure, ML research, 
      and whatever catches my attention at 2am.
    </p>

    <p>
      I operate a self-hosted cloud across a few VPS nodes, build with Rust, TypeScript, 
      Python and use Claude Code as my primary development tool. Most of what I do lives at the 
      intersection of systems programming and creative experimentation.
    </p>

    <p>
      When I'm not writing code, I'm probably photographing something, going down a ribit hole, or reading about 
      quantum computing and any other research paper that catches my curiosity. 
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h2>COLOPHON</h2>

    <p>
      This site is built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>, 
      hosted on <a href="https://pages.github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Pages</a>, 
      and set in Instrument Serif, Source Serif 4, and JetBrains Mono.
    </p>

    <p>
      The design takes cues from <a href="https://pi.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pi.dev</a> 
      (typography, whitespace) and <a href="https://opencode.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">opencode.ai</a> 
      (card layout). Posts are written in Markdown and live in the repo.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }
</style>
